text: Eileen Díaz (born 1 November 1979) is a Puerto Rican gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Puerto Rican female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Puerto Rico Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
